lothing and shanshan sports  original brands  such as firs mgb firs  design elteno lafancy letutu rosew bellson etc and  licensed or distributed brands such as marco azzali renoma paris lubiam  le coq sportif callaway golf apparel pinky  dianne munsingwear dunhill sports smalto le coq sportif golf collection qua etc in total the group comprises  listed companies  factories  fashion apparel companies and nearly 3 franchising shops at home and abroadless productservice highlights   suit jacket contact supplier womens suit contact supplier business suit contact supplier womens contact supplier   other productsservices   bespoke suit contact supplier tuxedo contact supplier mens casual shirt contact supplier mens shirt contact supplier   all productsservices company profile year of establishment  nature of business exporter manufacturer industry garments textiles  accessories productservice range textile garments annual turnover us    major markets • hong kong • middle east • north america • western europe company location contact information company ningbo shanshan co ltd contact person mrs susan zhu position manager office address 3 myunlin road wangchun indl zone ningbo zhejiang china countryregion ningbo zhejiang china telephone fax website wwwhktdccomemnbshanshan       wwwfirscomcn more contact supplier contact this supplier contact this supplier email your message please enter your message contact this supplier email your message add more details i would like to know more about your company and your products i would like to know more about your company and your products submit   font print this page email this page ﻿ newsletter ﻿ rss feeds mobile device ﻿ manage your hktdc esubscription ﻿ suppliers regional websites   hktdccom home  about hktdc  contact hktdc  advertise with hktdc  terms of use  privacy statement  hyperlink policy  site map  icp5 browse by   china suppliers  hong kong suppliers  asian suppliers  products   copyright  7   hong kong trade developme